              How customer reviews and ratings work

              Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

              To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

              • Alastair G. Stell
                5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to configure although requires an account with the manufacturer
                Reviewed in the United States on September 10, 2022
                Verified Purchase
                The included instructions to configure this lamp to work with Alexa were clear, unambiguous and worked perfectly.

                You get a range of voice commands that allow you both to turn the light on and off, as well as change color, brightness and modes. Yes, you do have to create an account with the manufacturer in order to link to Alexa but this has not created any secondary problems (such as unwanted emails).

                The light output is even and, as mood lighting, very effective. You aren't going to use this light for primary illumination (in my opinion) but as mood lighting it is highly effective. We are using this lamp to reflect off the corner of a room. The white light can be set to a variety of 'temperatures' although for watching TV we typically have it set to red light (which helps preserve night vision). The white light appears to be true white rather than a composite or RGB (which tends to create fringe colors).

                If I had any complaint it would simply be the manual controller (which we rarely use). It is complex and somewhat arcane in operation. Yes, it gets the job done, but you'll probably prefer to use Alexa (or Google) voice command instead!

                Kudos for a well built, well thought-out product that represents exceptional value for money. I have no hesitation in recommending this product to friends.
